name: Passinho da Siriema
description: Passinho da siriema is a frame by frame animation that was created for the video mapping Luvinha Goes To Cerrado. https://www.instagram.com/tv/CEpVciHBCR_/ Siriema is on of the symbols of the cerrado, a Brazilian bioma. In this piece, the animal is dancing a dance move from brazilian funk: siriema. Brazilian funk is a symbol of popular and street culture:, the passinho. So passinho da siriema is where the brazilian funk meets the nature. @soualuv
